{
  "nbformat": 4,
  "nbformat_minor": 5,
  "metadata": {
    "kernelspec": {
      "name": "maxima",
      "display_name": "Maxima",
      "language": "maxima"
    },
    "aximar": {}
  },
  "cells": [
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "# Event Detection with CVODE\n\nSUNDALS CVODE includes a rootfinding feature: given event functions $g_i(t, y)$, the solver detects zero crossings to high accuracy without requiring the user to manually bracket or bisect.\n\nPass events as the 8th argument in expression mode:\n```\nnp_cvode(rhs, vars, y0, tspan, rtol, atol, method, [g1, g2, ...])\n```\n\nWhen events are present, `np_cvode` returns `[trajectory, events_list]` where each event is `[t_event, [y_values], [indices]]`.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "load(\"numerics\")$\nload(\"numerics-sundials\")$\nload(\"ax-plots\")$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 1,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## 1. Bouncing Ball\n\nFree-fall with gravity: $\\dot{h} = v$, $\\dot{v} = -g$.\n\nEvent: $h = 0$ (ball hits ground). We detect the impact, then could use the event time and velocity to restart with a coefficient of restitution.\n\nDrop from $h = 10\\,$m, $v_0 = 0$. Expected impact at $t = \\sqrt{2h/g} \\approx 1.43\\,$s.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "g : 9.81$\ntspan1 : np_linspace(0.0, 3.0, 300)$\n\n[traj1, events1] : np_cvode(\n    [v, -g], [t, h, v], [10.0, 0.0], tspan1,\n    1e-12, 1e-12, adams, [h])$\n\nprintf(true, \"Number of events: ~d~%\", length(events1))$\nev1 : first(events1)$\nprintf(true, \"Impact time: ~,6f s  (exact: ~,6f)~%\",\n       first(ev1), sqrt(2*10.0/g))$\nprintf(true, \"Impact velocity: ~,4f m/s~%\", second(ev1)[2])$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 2,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "stdout",
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "Number of events: 1\no114Impact time: 1.427843 s  (exact: 1.427843)\no114Impact velocity: -14.0071 m/s\no114$$\\mathbf{false}$$\nfalse"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "t1 : np_slice(traj1, all, 0)$\nh1 : np_slice(traj1, all, 1)$\n\nax_draw2d(\n  color=\"#2563eb\", line_width=2, name=\"h(t)\",\n  lines(t1, h1),\n  color=\"#dc2626\", marker_size=8, name=\"impact\",\n  points([first(ev1)], [second(ev1)[1]]),\n  title=\"Bouncing Ball (single bounce)\",\n  xlabel=\"t (s)\", ylabel=\"h (m)\",\n  grid=true, showlegend=true\n)$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 3,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "data": {
            "application/x-maxima-plotly": [
