    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## 5. Multiple Simultaneous Events\n\nMonitor two event functions at once: a linear ramp $\\dot{y} = 1$ crossing thresholds at $y = 0.3$ and $y = 0.7$.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "[traj5, events5] : np_cvode(\n    [1], [t, y], [0.0], [0.0, 0.5, 1.0],\n    1e-12, 1e-12, adams, [y - 0.3, y - 0.7])$\n\nfor ev in events5 do\n  printf(true, \"t = ~,6f, y = ~,6f, event indices = ~a~%\",\n         first(ev), second(ev)[1], third(ev))$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 10,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "stdout",
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "t = 0.300000, y = 0.300000, event indices = [0]\no185t = 0.700000, y = 0.700000, event indices = [1]\no185$$\\mathbf{done}$$\nfalse"
          ]
        }
      ]
